/* IMPORTS */
const expect = require('chai').expect
const Homescreen = require('./home.screen')
const Morescreen = require('./more.screen')
// const ProfileScreen = require('./profile.screen')
const allure = require('@wdio/allure-reporter')
// const ConfigScreen = require('./configureIP.screen')
// const { expect } = require('chai')

/* GETTERS AND METHODS */
class SortingScreen {

    get sortingScreenText() {
        return $('~SORTING')
    }

    get rejectionTab() {
        return $("//android.view.View[contains(@content-desc,'Rejection') and contains(@content-desc,'Tab 1 of 2')]")
    }

    get manualTab() {
        return $("//android.view.View[contains(@content-desc,'Manual') and contains(@content-desc,'Tab 2 of 2')]")
    }

    get awbNoTextfield() {
        return $("//android.widget.EditText[contains(@text,'AWB No.')]")
    }

    get sortSearchResults() {
        return $("//android.view.View[contains(@content-desc,'Sort id')]")
    }

    get searchBtn() {
        return $("~Search")
    }

    get fieldCantBeEmpty() {
        return $("~This field cannot be empty")
    }

    get nulltext() {
        return $("~null")
    }

    async verifySortingScreenComponents() {
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More button not displayed" })
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).click()
        await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More screen not displayed" })
        expect(await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.eq("More", "More screen expected text doesnt match with actual")
        await allure.addStep("More Screen is displayed")
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting Button not displayed" })
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortingScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting screen not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Sorting screen is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Rejection tab not displayed" })
        expect(await (await this.rejectionTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Rejection", "Rejection tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Rejection Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB Text field not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("AWB Text field is displayed")
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search button not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Search button is displayed")
        expect(await (await this.manualTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Manual", "Manual tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Manual Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.manualTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB Text field not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("AWB Text field is displayed")
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search button not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Search button is displayed")
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await driver.back()
    }

    async verifySortingParcelDetailsInRejectionTab(awbNo) {
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More button not displayed" })
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).click()
        await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More screen not displayed" })
        expect(await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.eq("More", "More screen expected text doesnt match with actual")
        await allure.addStep("More Screen is displayed")
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting Button not displayed" })
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortingScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting screen not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Sorting screen is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Rejection tab not displayed" })
        expect(await (await this.rejectionTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Rejection", "Rejection tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Rejection Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB text field not displayed" })
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).setValue(awbNo)
        expect((await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]).to.eq(awbNo, `Actual AWB no "${(await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]}" doesnt match with entered AWB no "${awbNo}"`)
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search Button not displayed" })
        await (await this.searchBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortSearchResults).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: `Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is not displayed` })
        // expect(await (await this.sortSearchResults).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain.oneOf(["HV","LMM","UNX","DNF"])
        await allure.addStep(`Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is "${await (await this.sortSearchResults).getAttribute('content-desc')}"`)
        await driver.back()
    }

    async verifySortingDetailsForInvalidAWBNoRejectionTab(awbNo) {
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More button not displayed" })
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).click()
        await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More screen not displayed" })
        expect(await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.eq("More", "More screen expected text doesnt match with actual")
        await allure.addStep("More Screen is displayed")
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting Button not displayed" })
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortingScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting screen not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Sorting screen is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Rejection tab not displayed" })
        expect(await (await this.rejectionTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Rejection", "Rejection tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Rejection Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB text field not displayed" })
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).setValue(awbNo)
        expect((await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]).to.eq(awbNo, `Actual AWB no "${(await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]}" doesnt match with entered AWB no "${awbNo}"`)
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search Button not displayed" })
        await (await this.searchBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortSearchResults).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: `Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is not displayed` })
        expect(await (await this.sortSearchResults).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("IBO","Sort ID IBO is not displayed")
        await allure.addStep(`Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is "${await (await this.sortSearchResults).getAttribute('content-desc')}"`)
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await driver.back()
    }

    async verifyBlankSearchFunctionality(){
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More button not displayed" })
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).click()
        await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More screen not displayed" })
        expect(await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.eq("More", "More screen expected text doesnt match with actual")
        await allure.addStep("More Screen is displayed")
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting Button not displayed" })
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortingScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting screen not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Sorting screen is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Rejection tab not displayed" })
        expect(await (await this.rejectionTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Rejection", "Rejection tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Rejection Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.rejectionTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB text field not displayed" })
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).clearValue()
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search Button not displayed" })
        await (await this.searchBtn).click()
        await (await this.fieldCantBeEmpty).waitForDisplayed({timeout:3000,timeoutMsg:"Error text not displayed"})
        await allure.addStep(`Displayed error text is "${await (await this.fieldCantBeEmpty).getAttribute('content-desc') }"`)
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await driver.back()
    }

    async verifySortingParcelDetailsInManualTab(awbNo) {
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More button not displayed" })
        await (await Homescreen.moreModuleBtn).click()
        await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "More screen not displayed" })
        expect(await (await Morescreen.moreScreenText).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.eq("More", "More screen expected text doesnt match with actual")
        await allure.addStep("More Screen is displayed")
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting Button not displayed" })
        await (await Morescreen.sortingBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortingScreenText).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Sorting screen not displayed" })
        await allure.addStep("Sorting screen is displayed")
        await (await this.manualTab).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Manual tab not displayed" })
        expect(await (await this.manualTab).getAttribute('content-desc')).to.contain("Manual", "Rejection tab not displayed")
        await allure.addStep("Rejection Tab is displayed")
        await (await this.manualTab).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "AWB text field not displayed" })
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).click()
        await (await this.awbNoTextfield).setValue(awbNo)
        expect((await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]).to.eq(awbNo, `Actual AWB no "${(await (await this.awbNoTextfield).getText()).split(',')[0]}" doesnt match with entered AWB no "${awbNo}"`)
        await driver.hideKeyboard()
        await (await this.searchBtn).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: "Search Button not displayed" })
        await (await this.searchBtn).click()
        await (await this.sortSearchResults).waitForDisplayed({ timeout: 5000, timeoutMsg: `Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is not displayed` })
        await allure.addStep(`Sort results for AWB No "${awbNo}" is "${await (await this.sortSearchResults).getAttribute('content-desc')}"`)
        await driver.back()
    }

}
module.exports = new SortingScreen()
